00073 static DerivedMesh *applyModifier(ModifierData *md, Object *ob, DerivedMesh *dm,
00074                            int useRenderParams, int isFinalCalc)
00075 {
00076     MultiresModifierData *mmd = (MultiresModifierData*)md;
00077     DerivedMesh *result;
00078     Mesh *me= (Mesh*)ob->data;
00079 
00080     if (mmd->totlvl) {
00081         if (!CustomData_get_layer(&me->ldata, CD_MDISPS)) {
00082             /* multires always needs a displacement layer */
00083             CustomData_add_layer(&me->ldata, CD_MDISPS, CD_CALLOC, NULL, me->totloop);
00084         }
00085     }
00086 
00087     result = multires_dm_create_from_derived(mmd, 0, dm, ob, useRenderParams);
00088 
00089     if (result == dm)
00090         return dm;
00091 
00092     if (useRenderParams || !isFinalCalc) {
00093         DerivedMesh *cddm;
00094         
00095         cddm= CDDM_copy(result);
00096 
00097         /* copy hidden flag to vertices */
00098         if (!useRenderParams) {
00099             struct MDisps *mdisps;
00100             mdisps = CustomData_get_layer(&me->ldata, CD_MDISPS);
00101             if (mdisps) {
00102                 subsurf_copy_grid_hidden(result, me->mpoly,
00103                                          cddm->getVertArray(cddm),
00104                                          mdisps);
00105 
00106                 mesh_flush_hidden_from_verts(cddm->getVertArray(cddm),
00107                                              cddm->getLoopArray(cddm),
00108                                              cddm->getEdgeArray(cddm),
00109                                              cddm->getNumEdges(cddm),
00110                                              cddm->getPolyArray(cddm),
00111                                              cddm->getNumPolys(cddm));
00112             }
00113         }
00114 
00115         result->release(result);
00116         result= cddm;
00117     }
00118 
00119     return result;
00120 }
